msgctxt "#31962"
msgid "This toggles the visibility of ratings in views of type List, LowList and TriPanel, except if sorted by rating."
msgstr "Ovim se mijenja vidljivost ocjena u prikazima tipa Lista, LowList i TriPanel, osim ako su sortirane po ocjeni."

